{"tid":562284,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想同一個完全唔識既女仔做朋友，應該點做先唔會令人覺得係痴漢","createTime":"2018-02-15T18:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T06:41:09.000Z","uid":106256,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"18e34286a421053ec956ecc0fa2572d0357710fc","tid":562284,"uid":106256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:02:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的，幾年前搬左屋，遇到個好合眼緣既女仔，唔識對方，但住埋同一個社區周不時撞到，你問我想唔想溝佢就梗係想啦，但一方面唔清楚佢感情狀況，二來小弟家貧，預左要慢慢捱驢仔，基於以上兩點我只係想同佢做到普通朋友，得閒吹下水，過時過節一兩句祝福就夠，要點開口先可以同佢做到朋友，而又唔會令人覺得係痴漢呢?<br />\n<br />\n利申本人窮，但肯捱，會一路做野一路學唔同既技能好似烹飪、攝影、打燈之類，無不良嚐好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nching們比啲意見或者屌兩句都可以<br />\n<br />\n附圖以表誠意<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/020011_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F16%2F020011_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&d=cVB6s5YCvdh7Ad8ClQUOCghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2bb847de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/16/020011_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"8fe5c9d594b7ece0ba5f91abfb9781903e5f6793","tid":562284,"uid":38904,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://jdailyhk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/how-much-%E8%A6%81%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%B2%E4%B8%80%E9%BB%9E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjdailyhk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fhow-much-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2581%25B2%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%25BB%259E.png&h=04b96b0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6569eb577067b211ef9fe120745fc52efb2d406d","tid":562284,"uid":106256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T18:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.instagram.com/svetabily/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsvetabily%2F&h=b723d022&s={SI